NAiLING my Thoughts• YOUR PATH vlog 3

🗣What’s for you is FOR YOU!  Many of us have the same goals, missions, visions, & even dreams! This is ok! But understand, having this in common does not mean the path/journey to get there will be the same!! 

🛑 STOP looking back, stop focusing on what others are doing! This is taking focus away from YOUR journey!

Now you’ve watched someone else reach the top, You try focusing back on your path, but there’s a wall, a dead end, or even worse your on a completely different thats not yours which will never take you to YOUR DESTINATION!

Walk YOUR Path except YOUR journey and trust YOU will ARRIVE AT YOUR DESTINATION!

Share this vlog with someone who needs to hear it!

NAILTAINMENT ☻︎ 
Whew my Life Partner gone be 1 lucky man… ANYWHO, in the beauty industry we make “fast” money! Have you ever stopped and took a deep look at your numbers?

Many of us roll into this industry from passion and survival and not to make money! 

But Once your ready to reach a certain level of success you develop a what does my family and I future look like attitude. 

I recently took a financial bootcamp with @lady_finace (highly recommend working with her) and I learned a-lot about how I do business and where those funds should be going to ensure my family and I are se!t set!

Beauty Pros are you putting a % away in reinvesting, retirement, savings, vacation is a special one because vacations create long lasting memories that are priceless.

For me The material stuff can wait! I know how to look like a million bucks with out spending it.
